chinna poove mella &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( english : please speak , little flower ) is a 1987 tamil drama film directed by the duo robert - rajasekhar . the film features prabhu , ramki , &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , sudha chandran and sabitha anand in lead roles . the film , produced by s. k. rajagopal , had musical score by s. a. rajkumar and was released on 17 april 1987 . the film became highly successful at the box office . the film also marked the debut of s. a. rajkumar , ramki and &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; .